public class Parameter<T extends java.lang.Comparable<? super T>>
extends java.lang.Object
implements Expression

An Expression representing name=Value. This is appropriate to represent various aspects of Widgets (or other parametric entities): e.g. Attributes with values, other aspects of ComponentDescription.
